title: Woman Elf
description: A female creature with pointed ears and a human-like face.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, the woman elf emoji is a whimsical character, often depicted with pointed ears and a playful, enchanting expression. She is rendered with Apple's signature glossy 3D shading and smooth, vibrant colors, bringing a touch of fantasy to your messages. Her attire is stylized and magical, suggesting a connection to nature, folklore, and a spirit of wonder that adds a unique charm to digital communication.
